USX Corp announced a public offeringof 250 mln dlrs of convertible exchangeable cumulativepreference stock underwritten by Morgan Stanley and Co Inc andFIrst Boston Corp.    USX said the proceeds will be used to redeem its currentlyoutstanding 2.25 dlrs convertible exchangeable cumulativepreference stock.    USX said the new stock will be offered at 50 dlrs a shareand will have a dividend of 3.50 dlrs a share per year. REUTER&#3;